column5: Hey All,  We had a small turn out for our get together, but I had a good time. It's nice to sit and talk fishin' with guys who are familiar with your fishin' spots.  Anyway, sorry there's no pictures because ironically we all forgot our cameras!  Take care guys,  Until the next one  Dave
Yep, I had a great time.  Great to meet all you guys!
Sure, Sure a likely story.. so what really happened
skunky beer...good food...cute waitresses...lots of Whopper stories lol...nuff said!
Ya it was nice to meet you guys .Send me a PM if you ever want to get out and do some fishing .Or talk fishing and look at waitresses again for that matter
It was definitely nice meeting you guys, we'll have to do it again, and get out on the water as well!  Andrew.
How in the hell do you forget a camera???
well that took longer then expected
